	(lib_symbols)
	(text "ANALOG INPUT  (2 ch balanced, +4 dBu)
Components:
 - J: 2x Neutrik NC3FAH1 female XLR (L,R)
 - precision 0.1% balanced attenuator: 0 dBFS = +24 dBu (~ -12.5 dB)  [D1/R7]
 - U: OPA1612 diff receiver + anti-alias + ADC driver (1 dual/ch)
 - C0G anti-alias caps
Outputs AINL_P/N, AINR_P/N -> PCM4202 differential inputs.
Runs on +5V analog + Vcom mid-rail bias."
